{"TopicId":223143,"ForumId":120,"TopicTitle":"A twin seat MK1 cockpit (Basically just a stretched Peregrine cockpit with an extra seat)","CreatedByName":"DibzNr","CreatedById":212219,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-20T04:43:12Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"DibzNr","CreatedById":212219,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-20T04:43:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\nPretty short suggestion post, there\u0027s currently no (good looking) option for a twin seat Mk1 cockpit, as your options are essentially limited to either:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022image.png?ex=65bdc157\u0026amp;is=65ab4c57\u0026amp;hm=7fc5dab1a3a6c9f63acb6f18c3f95e7d418c0660a3d5b4081b7563041b826c83\u0026amp;\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsAttachLink_image ipsAttachLink_left\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.33\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 style=\u0022width:600px;height:auto;float:left;\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1039965578754007060/1198122294699118672/image.png?ex=65bdc157\u0026amp;is=65ab4c57\u0026amp;hm=7fc5dab1a3a6c9f63acb6f18c3f95e7d418c0660a3d5b4081b7563041b826c83\u0026amp;\u0022\u003E\u00A0or\u003Cimg alt=\u0022image.png?ex=65bdc194\u0026amp;is=65ab4c94\u0026amp;hm=ccfee7c6451be12376575e50bfa073ea25e97fba93f1ae1353a2fe1e6ed8f26d\u0026amp;\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsAttachLink_image ipsAttachLink_right\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.33\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 style=\u0022width:600px;height:auto;float:right;\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1039965578754007060/1198122551222739035/image.png?ex=65bdc194\u0026amp;is=65ab4c94\u0026amp;hm=ccfee7c6451be12376575e50bfa073ea25e97fba93f1ae1353a2fe1e6ed8f26d\u0026amp;\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\nNeither of which are particularly pretty, a twin seat stretched variant of the Peregrine cockpit would work wonders here for plane designs, something akin to the F-14\u0027s cockpit perhaps?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022image.png?ex=65bdc3b6\u0026amp;is=65ab4eb6\u0026amp;hm=952\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002295.90\u0022 height=\u0022257\u0022 width=\u0022268\u0022 src=\u0022https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1039965578754007060/1198124843074330664/image.png?ex=65bdc3b6\u0026amp;is=65ab4eb6\u0026amp;hm=9525a5f8385732ea965c3e832508090c61d8525cfcbb64a29350be9ef5f3fa3d\u0026amp;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022image.png?ex=65bdc402\u0026amp;is=65ab4f02\u0026amp;hm=c62\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002255.15\u0022 height=\u0022166\u0022 width=\u0022301\u0022 src=\u0022https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1039965578754007060/1198125159098351675/image.png?ex=65bdc402\u0026amp;is=65ab4f02\u0026amp;hm=c62ea7f7f6eddda3bb74e076c5042ec5d6b9a0191a5d76d06cdcc20e97f410f2\u0026amp;\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222024-01-22T20:49:55Z\u0022 title=\u002201/22/2024 08:49  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Jan 22\u0022\u003EJanuary 22\u003C/time\u003E by DibzNr\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lowi_Sace","CreatedById":224820,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-20T10:03:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en-us\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en-us\u0022\u003EI think in terms how they organized the cockpit is very nice. Having one for every size. A way they could change it is by bringing part variants back. So selecting cockpit and then choose the regular or extended (2 seater) version. The same can be done for crew pods, after selecting the size having a few pod designs to choose from (like crew dragon style for M), with all having their own advantage\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-20T10:15:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am actually quite fond of this one, though it doesn\u0027t mean you can\u0027t have a 2-seater dedicated one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022image.png?ex=65bdc194\u0026amp;is=65ab4c94\u0026amp;hm=ccf\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 style=\u0022width:425px;height:auto;\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1039965578754007060/1198122551222739035/image.png?ex=65bdc194\u0026amp;is=65ab4c94\u0026amp;hm=ccfee7c6451be12376575e50bfa073ea25e97fba93f1ae1353a2fe1e6ed8f26d\u0026amp;\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI (as always) like the idea of a toggleable / procedural part to address this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222024-01-20T10:16:34Z\u0022 title=\u002201/20/2024 10:16  AM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Jan 20\u0022\u003EJanuary 20\u003C/time\u003E by Superfluous J\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jeq","CreatedById":172375,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-20T10:56:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want to be Maverick puking at backseat while real pilot at front does all the flying.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}